Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:41.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Where are my glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.81,0:00:44.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've been playing the same fighting games lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.47,0:00:43.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If I don't have my glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:46.32,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}BON-BON Cheerleaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.32,0:00:47.89,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's get! Cherry pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.89,0:00:49.48,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}RAN-RAN Welcome party
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:51.09,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Look up! Sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:51.76,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:54.16,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The presence... of asteroids!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.16,0:00:55.76,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As they confoundedly collide and melt...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:00:57.54,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sing loudly! Like a Sirenger
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:00:58.70,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:03.15,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll be the one with the last laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:10.05,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because I'm wearing a sailor uniform {\fnaquafont\fs34.5}←{\rs}And that's that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:12.31,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even though it's only Monday!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.31,0:01:15.80,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm feeling horrible. What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:22.85,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The summer clothes are so much better! {\fnaquafont\fs34.5}←{\rs}Oh, so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:25.96,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's getting close to 3 picts. Yet, I'm still hesitating.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.96,0:01:30.00,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Try your best! Get your spirits up! My Darlin' darlin' PLEASE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:02.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.41,0:00:03.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.02,0:00:05.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing around and start!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.76,0:01:33.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They bought me another cell phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:35.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put it in the wash this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.43,0:01:38.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put it somewhere obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:39.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.94,0:01:41.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a hand, Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:42.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.86,0:01:51.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ba.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:52.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,L.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.97,0:01:54.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.87,0:01:58.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:01.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,C.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.32,0:02:01.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.37,0:02:03.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:05.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Vinegar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.43,0:02:06.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.47,0:02:08.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll input it for you, so hand it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:09.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's irritating!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.89,0:02:10.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.89,0:02:12.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.14,0:02:13.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.72,0:02:17.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:18.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cousin Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.10,0:02:18.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.26,0:02:20.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatcha doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.69,0:02:22.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Playing a dating sim that just came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:30.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm gonna borrow some random manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.32,0:02:31.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.24,0:02:35.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This game is age restricted...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:36.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but did she not notice...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.89,0:02:38.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...or is she letting it slide?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.71,0:02:41.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which one is it, officer?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:43.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:46.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...we beef things up during Traffic Safety Awareness Week.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:48.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like detailed checks...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:51.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and explanations of traffic laws...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:53.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.26,0:02:55.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes, they start yelling at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:57.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But when I look at how she usually acts...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:57.33,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Scary! Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.73,0:03:00.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...she's not very convincing when talking about laws or safety!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:02.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally shocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.48,0:03:09.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've heard that colds are lasting longer this year...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.07,0:03:11.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...so I need to get better quickly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.94,0:03:14.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Based on my number...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:17.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...I'll probably be here a while.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.57,0:03:19.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll read while I wait.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:21.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Ando.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:23.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Shigeo Ando.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:31.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Takara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.80,0:03:33.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Miyuki Takara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:38.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Miyuki Takara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.39,0:03:39.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.89,0:03:44.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the next person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.04,0:03:45.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Mariko Nishiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:53.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.82,0:03:54.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:55.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did they call me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.51,0:03:56.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What time is it?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:59.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need to pay more attention to my surroundings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:04.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We will soon arrive at the final stop, Kamata.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:08.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where am I?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.92,0:04:13.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I taught Tsukasa how to text message the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:16.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She still had no idea after all that messing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:19.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And she must have been really happy about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.89,0:04:22.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...since she's constantly texting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:26.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Must suck for the recipient.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.86,0:04:30.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:33.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the type to start off excited...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:34.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and eventually lose interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.73,0:04:38.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people are just childish like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:40.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She sent another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:43.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If she doesn't get bored, you'll be pretty swamped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:46.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And does she even have that much to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:49.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're practically together 24/7.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.09,0:04:51.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And she apparently learned how to use symbols.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.59,0:04:52.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.38,0:04:56.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we buy soy cream-man on the way home again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:04:59.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all the stuff at the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:03.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell she's having fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:05.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't even seen half of these before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:12.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she's finally gotten the hang of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:36.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:39.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how you feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:41.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but could you stop spamming family members?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:43.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:44.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:49.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure about how to use text messaging on a cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.27,0:05:50.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, hey, hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:52.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really easy, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:54.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:56.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:06:01.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess some people get all\Nsnobby after they've learned something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:03.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:07.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That smell is beyond words.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:08.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:09.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It just stinks too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:10.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:14.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a lot of stuff saved on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.79,0:06:15.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:16.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop going through that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:19.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got messages that shouldn't be seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:20.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:21.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:22.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:24.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:25.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.97,0:06:31.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not picking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:34.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll call her house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:39.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:41.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.24,0:06:43.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You should answer your cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:45.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.16,0:06:48.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't ring so I didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:49.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:51.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that defeat the purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:54.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And where is that thing anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:57.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your cell phone really serves no purpose, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:06:58.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:07:00.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,About next weekend...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.09,0:07:02.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's talking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:02.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:03.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:05.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.31,0:07:06.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.77,0:07:07.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been on the phone too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.77,0:07:08.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't wait any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:09.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:12.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I got in trouble for being on the phone too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:13.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.90,0:07:17.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I figured you guys would be relaxed about that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:19.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like it's pretty strict.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.36,0:07:20.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:22.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We were in the middle of a fighting game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:25.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me that earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:30.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:33.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...my point cards shine with an invisible magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.83,0:07:38.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You end up making unplanned purchases, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.05,0:07:40.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You really wing everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:41.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I kinda understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:48.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:51.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In this city, we have Ani**te and Ga**rs...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.35,0:07:53.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Two anime stores...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:56.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There exists a person who\Nbuys the same thing from both stores...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.86,0:07:58.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Legendary Girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:07:58.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:05.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Legendary Girl A shift!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:21.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.84,0:08:26.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The DVD for Haruhi Vol. 5's in stock!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:28.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Limited edition!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:30.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Regular edition!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:31.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:36.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And we've got loads of related items!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:37.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:41.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just display every item we have in stock.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:43.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She'll buy whatever she can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:47.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted a limited Aquarian Age bookmark today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:49.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Need to go to Gamers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:51.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:58.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll do a sleepover this weekend and play all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.67,0:09:03.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We usually do stuff at our place...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:05.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but can we go to your house?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:08.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to go over every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:13.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that you can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:17.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but my dad's usually home because of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:18.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:22.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So that just increases the burden on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:23.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What burden?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.65,0:09:28.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kinda looking forward to seeing what Konata's house is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:31.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:33.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.37,0:09:34.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to impose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.58,0:09:36.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for having us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.33,0:09:37.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:39.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard a lot about you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:42.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're shrine maidens who live at a temple, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.92,0:09:43.67,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What have you been telling him?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:45.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So do you usually wear yellow hakamas?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:45.52,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And like, that's the first thing he has to say?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:46.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:50.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kona-chan's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:53.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Crazy as expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:56.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:00.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This door...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:05.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably hides a stash of stuff you don't want seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:06.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A door that must never be opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:07.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:10.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I share most of that stuff with Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.95,0:10:13.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so he handles storage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.41,0:10:16.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You share...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:18.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:20.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad's an author, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:26.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then have you ever gotten hooked on a\Nlight novel or dating sim your dad wrote?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:26.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.47,0:10:29.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't write any of that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:30.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:33.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't expect that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.39,0:10:33.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.97,0:10:35.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He likes that kind of stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:37.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so wouldn't he want to write them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:39.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's like a lurker...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:40.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,According to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.23,0:10:43.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...he plays dating sims and life sims on his own time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:47.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so he doesn't feel the need to bring it to the workplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.07,0:10:51.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been at a loss for words for a while now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.37,0:10:52.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Guess that's the Izumi family for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:58.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad was being all clingy the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.99,0:11:02.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I tried saying, "You're annoying, Dad!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.83,0:11:05.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a little harsh, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:05.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:09.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you at least say, "I hate you, Dad!" or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.34,0:11:09.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:11.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not quite right either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.88,0:11:17.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But your way of thinking wouldn't fulfill his expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.52,0:11:17.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:19.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:24.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.65,0:11:27.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:33.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even TV shows are starting to look like 2ch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.41,0:11:34.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:36.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:39.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:43.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,For someone hardcore, you don't use much of that lingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.29,0:11:44.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In normal situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:48.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In chatrooms, I'm like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:49.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:51.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this even Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:53.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can read this, you've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:11:59.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything I can help with?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.14,0:12:01.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then serve the salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:07.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:10.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:12.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:13.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A job well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:17.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing for someone who does housework on a daily basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.24,0:12:20.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you did more housework, you might get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:21.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:24.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.29,0:12:25.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:29.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a scene out of my dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:36.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A man eating a meal with three high school girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:36.20,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}H-Heaven on earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:37.41,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:40.92,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tohsaka... Tohsaka's your sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:39.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...happens way more than it should in dating sims.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:41.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.27,0:12:48.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It gets chilly when it's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.15,0:12:50.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Should have put on a jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:53.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A shooting star!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:13:02.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't make my wish three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.33,0:13:04.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty hard when they come out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:10.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll pull it off one day and have my wish granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.05,0:13:12.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa's a dreamer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:15.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's impossible from a practical standpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:20.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a superstition because you know it isn't going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:23.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does this one have no dreams...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:25.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Want a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:27.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:29.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You switched hairstyles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:30.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,For fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:32.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,While we were taking a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:38.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why do the same parts feel so different on different people?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:40.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A photo album.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:41.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:42.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:45.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kona-chan's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:49.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:50.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And like...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.88,0:13:52.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you sure are close with your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:55.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:56.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.37,0:13:57.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So young!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:58.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't I look like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:13:59.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She was legal, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:03.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wonder when I look at Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:07.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What did Mom ever see in Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.81,0:14:08.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.77,0:14:11.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You look just like your mom, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.73,0:14:12.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then in that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:15.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What would be your type?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:16.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:20.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When you put it that way, I don't really have one...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.28,0:14:21.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:22.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Spill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:26.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means Mom was okay with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.54,0:14:29.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And she said something about knowing Dad since they were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:31.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.38,0:14:33.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't let Dad flounder around by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.72,0:14:35.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even hold back for your parents, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.67,0:14:38.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I look at my mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:41.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In manga and games these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:43.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...a lot of middle schoolers look mature...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:46.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and a lot of adults look really young.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.18,0:14:49.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:51.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you want me to say something?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.31,0:14:55.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish Yuki-chan could have come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.11,0:14:56.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she's busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:57.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:15:00.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll text her so she isn't lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:04.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki's really considerate, so stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:06.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:09.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.21,0:15:13.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm working hard to finish my homework right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:15.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please invite me again next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:19.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot we had homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:21.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something, Kagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:23.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Our class didn't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:24.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go to sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.39,0:15:25.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:28.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That shooting star.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:32.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It might work if I use short wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:33.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:36.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:40.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Studying how to say wishes faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:43.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop escaping reality and get your homework done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:47.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:51.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get this part in class earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:53.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That part?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:55.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata leads to Kona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:57.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki leads to Yuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:02.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what nickname would you use for Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.26,0:16:03.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:03.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Gami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:07.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Kyo-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.47,0:16:08.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pronounce Kagami a different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.89,0:16:10.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:11.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good naming sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.35,0:16:13.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels strong like her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:16.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And you could use this Kyo-chan, too
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.23,0:16:19.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That wasn't my intention...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:22.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We probably shouldn't tell Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:25.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what nickname would you give yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.87,0:16:26.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.74,0:16:27.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kasa-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:30.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi-chan, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:32.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's harder with my first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:33.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:37.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You do give off a "hi-hi" image all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.09,0:16:39.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't my intention...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:39.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.25,0:16:43.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll start calling you Hi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:44.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:46.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:49.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it feels kind of weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:51.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...if I chose it myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:52.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.85,0:16:53.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.39,0:16:55.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:16:57.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Want revenge, Sebastian?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:16:58.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Name's Shiraishi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:16:59.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.07,0:17:00.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:02.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyo-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.24,0:17:04.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she calling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.86,0:17:07.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too hard to understand, so stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.16,0:17:09.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how do you want me to call you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:11.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't Kagami work?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:12.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A nickname would be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:15.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Kona-chan or Yuki-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:20.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then call me Kagami the Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:22.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:24.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami the Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:26.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She really did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:27.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:28.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just trying it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.97,0:17:32.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait, Kagami the Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:35.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kagami the Great?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.27,0:17:37.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:35.88,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:38.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:39.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just call me normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:47.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:48.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:53.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're already on the booming tenth episode of Lucky Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:55.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your navigator, Akira Kogami.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:56.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:58.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the assistant, Minoru Shiraishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:00.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And right off the bat...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.25,0:18:02.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...we have our fourth character introduction...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.76,0:18:04.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami Hiiragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:08.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She serves as a punch line character in the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:10.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't she just a tsundere?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:13.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What an obvious setup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:14.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg to differ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.89,0:18:20.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The classification of Kagami Hiiragi as a tsundere is a bit hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.40,0:18:21.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:26.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,First, do we comprehend the true\Nmeaning of the qualities of a tsundere?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:29.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, unfortunately...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.20,0:18:31.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...the word tsundere has suffered misuse and decay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:34.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and one could say that the definition has evolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:37.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To begin with, the word tsundere was born in the year 2002...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.29,0:18:38.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...an Internet term...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:40.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the original definition was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:42.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...a character who starts off hostile...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:43.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and eventually becomes affectionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:44.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.17,0:18:44.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:47.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...it was supposed to describe a change over time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:48.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:49.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.97,0:18:52.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...it is used to describe the multiple faces of a character.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:53.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:54.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...hostile on the outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.81,0:18:56.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and affectionate on the inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.02,0:18:58.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...would be how the word is currently understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:00.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I declare here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:03.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is plainly a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.11,0:19:05.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We must bring back the true meaning of tsundere...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.90,0:19:09.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and restore this depraved nation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:10.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Rise up, citizens!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.57,0:19:13.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, Sebastian.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:14.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:17.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So if Kagami's not a tsundere, what is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:17.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You meant me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.87,0:19:21.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get this complicated stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.00,0:19:22.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but if you insist...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.92,0:19:26.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...do you have a replacement for\Nwhat's currently known as tsundere?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:27.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:29.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.49,0:19:30.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe cool-dere...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:32.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.18,0:19:32.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Deretsun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:35.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You got no sense at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.60,0:19:37.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsundere's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:38.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:40.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.43,0:19:42.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:46.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ask the viewers to come up with a new expression!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:47.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:48.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Delegating, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.61,0:19:50.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So, everyone in front of the TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:52.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:55.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to come up with a new word\Nto describe characters like Kagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:19:58.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And rewrite the modern lexicon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:01.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dubbed the Complete Tsundere Debate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,0:20:04.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can find more details on the radio show and home page!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:06.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're waiting for your passionate ideas!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.42,0:20:10.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.88,0:20:12.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:13.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots and lots...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:15.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots and lots...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:17.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bee.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.18,0:20:19.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.77,0:20:20.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Fast forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:25.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, I talked a lot today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:26.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The most ever, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.94,0:20:29.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.03,0:20:29.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:32.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.03,0:20:33.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:34.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.28,0:20:36.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the most I've ever spoken.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:37.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I did a fair job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.20,0:20:42.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to dinner with the\Nexecutive and producer from your studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:44.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:47.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna discuss your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:49.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, h-hold on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.37,0:20:50.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:56.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No point in telling you about how your future's looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.18,0:20:56.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.89,0:20:59.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And aren't you still working at CoCo*chi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.93,0:21:01.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's only during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.39,0:21:03.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And it doesn't pay much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.23,0:21:04.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And the grill place?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:05.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:07.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or that doesn't even matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:09.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's intruding into my privacy, so stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:15.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm next.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:16.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.43,0:21:17.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:19.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This works!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:20.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Yuki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:21.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.56,0:21:23.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then sing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:24.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Kona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:25.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:26.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.92,0:21:28.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They chose a song?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:37.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This song was popular when we were in preschool, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.76,0:21:38.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't really know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.93,0:21:39.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.85,0:21:41.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:42.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.31,0:21:44.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Our older sisters sang it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.60,0:21:47.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Songs sung by parents and older siblings...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.56,0:21:49.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...while from an earlier generation...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:52.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...tend to be memorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:24.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Caved, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.12,0:22:25.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.50,0:22:26.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really high.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.78,0:22:43.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, next time on Lucky Star:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:44.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.66,0:22:47.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When you go out to eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.08,0:22:49.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and order something with liquids...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.38,0:22:52.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and a few drops splatter onto your clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.01,0:22:53.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's pretty depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.63,0:22:56.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And it really sucks if it's curry sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.55,0:22:59.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And you happen to be wearing your favorite clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.39,0:23:02.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaves you down the whole day!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.61,0:23:05.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And when you buy a box lunch\Nwith sauce from a convenience store...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:09.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and you carry it level so the contents don't spill...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.81,0:23:11.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but once you open the bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.32,0:23:14.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you discover that it spilled inside and everything's a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.53,0:23:16.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes you lose your appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.78,0:23:21.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And when you ask them to bag\Nhot and cold items separately...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.16,0:23:25.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and they bag the cold drinks with your magazines...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.20,0:23:27.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the paper sucks up the condensation...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.79,0:23:29.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the magazine's all soggy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.71,0:23:32.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and you're like what was the\Npoint in bagging them separately then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.54,0:23:34.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:36.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The Many Ways to Spend Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.42,0:23:37.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to next time!
