Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.32,0:21:31.45,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:38.04,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Your battered figure is reflected in the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.04,0:21:42.00,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I walked aimlessly...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:46.67,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Sighed inwardly...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.67,0:21:48.92,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.92,0:21:55.47,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been searching for something...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.47,0:22:04.14,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,...to bind this fragile, ephemeral passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.14,0:22:12.95,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can I no longer dream innocently as I once did?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.95,0:22:17.28,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no place for me in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.28,0:22:23.29,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Love spills from my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.55,0:22:34.43,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The crowd—
